data.description: This charming, updated Cape Cod in Jackson Local Schools has a fresh look with new siding and a new roof and new gutters with leaf guard.  Step inside to new flooring and an updated eat in kitchen.  Two bedrooms and a full bath for first floor convenience.  The lower level has new flooring and a full bath perfect for entertaining.  Storage galore in this home!!!  Enjoy the double lot and convenience of a shed  with a completely fenced in back yard.  Covered patio for entertainment along with a large fire pit area for evening fires and cookouts.  The two plus garage has work benches and extra storage space.  The furnace and air conditioning was recently updated as well.  Reverse Osmosis System for excellent water!  This home shows well and will not disappoint.
